<chapter line="1">Yamakappakaraṇa-aṭṭhakathā</chapter>
<gatha1 line="2">Saṅkhepeneva <pageBreak edition="M" number="0.0287" /><pageBreak edition="P" number="0.0052" /><pageBreak edition="V" number="0.0286" /> devānaṃ, devadevo surālaye;</gatha1>
<gathalast line="3">Kathāvatthuppakaraṇaṃ, desayitvā raṇañjaho.</gathalast>
<gatha1 line="4">Yamassa visayātīto, nānāyamakamaṇḍitaṃ;</gatha1>
<gathalast line="5">Abhidhammappakaraṇaṃ, chaṭṭhaṃ chaṭṭhāna desako.</gathalast>
<gatha1 line="6">Yamakaṃ ayamāvatta-nīlāmalatanūruho;</gatha1>
<gatha2 line="7">Yaṃ desayi anuppatto, tassa saṃvaṇṇanākkamo;</gatha2>
<gathalast line="8">Idāni yasmā tasmāssa, hoti saṃvaṇṇanā ayanti.</gathalast>
